PrecisOrder directing that a PROCLAMATION do issue authorizing the minting of a ONE-CENT COPPER-PLATED SILVER COIN replicating the first domestically- produced one-cent coin struck by the Royal Canadian Mint in 1908, except that the word "CANADA" will be engraved under the effigy of The Queen.
